2627.name: Mark of Challenger
2627.description: A mark given to those who have passed the Trial of the Challenger. An item for occupational change.

2628.name: Letter of Kash
2628.description: Kash's introduction letter. Take this letter to Martien in Town of Giran.

2629.name: Watcher's 1st Eye
2629.description: An item obtained from the monster, Gorr. Take this to Martien in Town of Giran.

2630.name: Watcher's 2nd Eye
2630.description: An item obtained from the monster, Baraham. Show this to Raldo and...

2631.name: Scroll of Shyslassys
2631.description: An ancient scroll obtained by slaying Shyslassys. Take this to Kash in the Town of Dion.

2632.name: Broken Key
2632.description: A key obtained by slaying Shyslassys. This key is needed in order to open the Chest of Shyslassys.

2633.name: Mark of Duty
2633.description: A mark given to those who have passed the Trial of Duty. An item for occupational change.

2634.name: Letter of Dustin
2634.description: A letter given by Dustin. Deliver the letter to Grand Master Hannavalt in Town of Giran.

2635.name: Knight's Tear
2635.description: Obtained from the spirit of Sir Herod. Take this to Sir Aaron Tanford.

2636.name: Mirror of Orpic
2636.description: This is needed in order to speak with the ghost of Sir Talianus. Use this to defeat the hangman tree.

2637.name: Tear of Confession
2637.description: Obtained from the ghost of Sir Talianus. Take this to Sir Kiel Nighthawk.

2638.name: Report Piece
2638.description: You may obtain this by hunting strains and ghouls. Gather 10 pieces and put them together to create Talianus's report.

2639.name: Report Piece
2639.description: The completed report. After speaking with Sir Kiel Nighthawk, deliver the report to the ghost of Sir Talianus.

2640.name: Tear of Loyalty
2640.description: This item can be obtained from Isael Silvershadow. Take it to Priest Dustin.

2641.name: Militas Article
2641.description: You can receive this item when you catch a Leto lizardman. Collect 20 of them and take them to Isael Silvershadow.

2642.name: Saints Ashes Urn
2642.description: An object received from Priest Dustin. Deliver this to Sir Windawood.

2643.name: Athebaldt's Skull
2643.description: You can obtain this item from a Breka orc overlord. Take it to Priest Dustin along with Athebaldt's ribs and Athebaldt's shin.

2644.name: Athebaldt's Ribs
2644.description: You can obtain this item from a Breka orc overlord. Take it to Priest Dustin along with Athebaldt's skull and Athebaldt's shin.

2645.name: Athebaldt's Shin
2645.description: You can obtain this item from a Breka orc overlord. Take it to Priest Dustin along with Athebaldt's ribs and Athebaldt's skull.

2646.name: Letter of Windawood
2646.description: A letter received from Sir Colin Windawood. Show this to Priest Dustin.

2647.name: Dufners Letter
2647.description: A letter sent from Master Dufner to Master Terry in the Town of Dion.

2648.name: Terry's 1st Order
2648.description: Investigate the neer ghoul berserkers of the Execution Grounds.

2649.name: Terry's 2nd Order
2649.description: Investigate the Ol Mahum captain, Turek orc warlord, ant captain and Turak bugbear warrior.

2650.name: Terry's Letter
2650.description: A letter sent by Master Terry to Trader Viktor of Hunters Village.

2651.name: Viktor's Letter
2651.description: A letter sent by Trader Viktor to Master Terry in the Town of Dion. The letter has Terry's seal.

2652.name: Hawkeye's Letter
2652.description: A letter sent by Hawkeye to Trader Viktor of the Hunters Village.

2653.name: Mysterious Spirit Ore
2653.description: A mysterious Spirit Ore obtained after slaying neer ghoul berserkers. Take this to Master Terry.

2654.name: Ol Mahum Spirit Ore
2654.description: A mysterious Spirit Ore obtained after slaying the Ol Mahum captain. Take this to Master Terry.

2655.name: Turek Spirit Ore
2655.description: A mysterious Spirit Ore obtained after slaying the Turek orc overlord. Take this to Master Terry.

2656.name: Ant Spirit Ore
2656.description: A mysterious Spirit Ore obtained after slaying the ant captain. Take this to Master Terry.

2657.name: Turak Bugbear Spirit Ore
2657.description: A mysterious Spirit Ore obtained after slaying the Turak bugbear warrior. Take this to Master Terry.

2658.name: Terry's Box
2658.description: A chest containing the mysterious Spirit Ore. Take this to Trader Viktor of the Hunters Village.

2659.name: Viktor's Request
2659.description: A request issued by Trader Viktor. "Please gather 10 medusa scales."

2660.name: Medusa Scales
2660.description: The scales of the medusa. Gather 10 of these and take them to Trader Viktor.

2661.name: Shilen's Spirit Ore
2661.description: Strange Spirit Ore obtained from the bodies of mutant species. They seem to be related to Shilen, the goddess of death.

2662.name: Analysis Request
2662.description: A request letter sent to Magister Marina of the Ivory Tower from Trader Viktor. The letter asks Marina to analyze the dark bezoar.

2663.name: Marina's Letter
2663.description: A letter sent by Magister Marina to Blacksmith Brunon of the Dwarven Village.

2664.name: Experiment Tools
2664.description: Experimental tools crafted by Blacksmith Brunon. Deliver these to Magister Marina of the Ivory Tower.

2665.name: Analysis Result
2665.description: A document where Magister Marina has organized the analyzed results of the Dark Bezoar. Deliver this to Master Terry in the Town of Dion.

2666.name: Terry's 3rd Order
2666.description: Master Terry's orders. The orders give instructions to come back for the next task after reaching level 36.

2667.name: List of Host
2667.description: A list of the bezoar hosts. "Marsh stakato drone, Breka orc overlord, ant warrior captain, Leto lizardman warrior"

2668.name: Abyss Spirit Ore
2668.description: The dark bezoar retrieved from the body of a marsh stakato drone. Take this to Master Terry.

2669.name: Abyss Spirit Ore
2669.description: The Spirit Ore retrieved from the body of the Breka orc overlord. Take this to Master Terry.

2670.name: Abyss Spirit Ore
2670.description: The Spirit Ore retrieved from the body of the ant captain. Take this to Master Terry.

2671.name: Abyss Spirit Ore
2671.description: The Spirit Ore retrieved from the body of the Leto lizardman warrior. Take this to Master Terry.

2672.name: Terry's Report
2672.description: A report detailing information about the Spirit Ore incident. Take this to Master Dufner of Town of Giran.

2673.name: Mark of Seeker
2673.description: A mark given to those who have passed the Trial of the Seeker. An occupation change related item.

2674.name: Mark of Scholar
2674.description: A mark given to those who have passed the Trial of the Scholar. An occupation change related item.

2675.name: Mirien's 1st Sigil
2675.description: A mark given by Magister Mirien while giving orders to complete High Priest Sylvain's request.

2676.name: Mirien's 2nd Sigil
2676.description: A mark given by Magister Mirien while giving orders to complete Grand Magister Jurek's request.

2677.name: Mirien's 3rd Sigil
2677.description: A mark given by Magister Mirien when giving orders to complete Elder Cronos's request.

2678.name: Mirien's Instruction
2678.description: A note that contains Magister Mirien's instructions. The note gives instructions to come back for the next task after reaching level 36.

2679.name: Maria's 1st Letter
2679.description: A letter sent by Maria to Captain Lucas in the Town of Dion.

2680.name: Maria's 2nd Letter
2680.description: A letter sent by Maria to Astrologer Creta of the village of Floran.

2681.name: Lucas's Letter
2681.description: A letter sent by Captain Lucas in the Town of Dion to Maria.

2682.name: Lucilla's Handbag
2682.description: The handbag left by Maria's friend Lucillas on the night of the theft. Take this to Astrologer Creta.

2683.name: Creta's 1st Letter
2683.description: A letter sent by the Astrologer Creta to Maria in the Town of Dion.

2684.name: Creta's Painting1
2684.description: A painting by Astrologer Creta. It contains a shadow presumed to be that of the thief. Take this to Maria.

2685.name: Creta's Painting2
2685.description: A painting by Astrologer Creta. It contains a shadow presumed to be that of the thief. Take this to Captain Lucas.

2686.name: Creta's Painting3
2686.description: A painting painted by Astrologer Creta. The shadow in the painting is that of a Leto lizardman warrior.

2687.name: Brown Scroll Scrap
2687.description: A scrap of a scroll that contains directions on how to create the crystal of purity. Gather 5 of these and take them to Maria.

2688.name: Crystal of Purity
2688.description: A crystal used to purify the earth. Take this to High Priest Sylvain in the Town of Dion.

2689.name: High Priest's Sigil
2689.description: A mark received from High Priest Sylvain. A proof given to those who are carrying out the orders of the High Priest.

2690.name: Grand Magister's Sigil
2690.description: A mark received from Grand Magister Jurek. A proof given to those who are carrying out the orders of the Grand Magister.

2691.name: Crono's Sigil
2691.description: A mark received from Elder Cronos. This signifies proof that someone is carrying out orders from Elder Cronos.

2692.name: Sylvain's Letter
2692.description: High Priest Sylvain's letter. Take this to Maria in the Town of Dion.

2693.name: Symbol of Sylvain
2693.description: A symbol given to those who have passed High Priest Sylvain's test. Take this to Magister Mirien in the Town of Dion.

2694.name: Jurek's List
2694.description: The list of evil creatures that Grand Magister Jurek asked you to investigate: Monster eye destroyer, Breka orc shaman, and shackle.

2695.name: Monster Eye Destroyer's Skin
2695.description: A beamer's skin. Gather 5 of these and take them to Grand Magister Jurek of Town of Giran.

2696.name: Shaman's Necklace
2696.description: A Breka orc shaman's necklace. Gather 5 of these and take them to Grand Magister Jurek in Town of Giran.

2697.name: Shackle's Scalp
2697.description: Skin of the shackle's head. Gather 2 of these and take them to Grand Magister Jurek of Town of Giran.

2698.name: Symbol of Jurek
2698.description: A symbol given to those who have passed Grand Magister Jurek's test. Take this to Magister Mirien in the Town of Dion.

2699.name: Cronos Letter
2699.description: A letter sent by Elder Cronos to Magister Dieter in the Town of Giran.
